# Note: the sqlx offline query cache under `.sqlx/` is INTENTIONALLY
# committed so CI can build without a live database. Regenerate with
# `cargo sqlx prepare --workspace` after changing any sqlx::query! /
# query_as! call. Do not add `.sqlx/` to this file.

